<p>Out of their minds, do you hear me? Or at least of what is left of them.</p>
<p>Check the stats if you don&#8217;t believe me. The number one place where Oregonians retire is Washington &#8211; FACT &#8211; by the numbers. We would not want retirees to stay would we? They are such a drain on our state services and they don&#8217;t contribute to the economy. Let them go to Washington &#8211; and spend their PERS checks up there. It makes perfect sense.</p>
